Active Directory------group / memberOf
ServiceNow---------------group
SAP----------------------role
Jira--------------------group
To yaha group = attribute name.

()2️⃣ FinanceGroup kya hai:-
entitlement.setValue("FinanceGroup");
Ye actual group ka naam hai jisme user ko add karna hai.

Example:-
Active Directory Groups
FinanceGroup
HRGroup
AdminGroup
ITSupportGroup

()3️⃣ setOperation(Add) kya karega:-
